Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Card
    A standard UNO card, used when determining what to do when the card is played
    Deck
    A deck of cards and can be shuffled and printed
    EventHandler
    Used to handel the action events (buttons)
    FileManager
    Used to create the Settings, Players, and instructions
    Hover
    Used to change the color of the buttons on hover
    MainGameLoop
    Controls the whole game, and calls other classes as needed
    MyFrame
    Used for the high level graphics such as the Buttons and holding all the button actions
    MyPannel
    Used for drawing the low level graphics and controlling the overall look of the game
    Player
    A player in the game, contains the basic functions for playing the game
    Settings  
    Setup
    Used for setting up the objects and functions
    Visuals
    Handels the graphical updates of the game
